window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Singularity has come. The machines have risen. </p> <p>Our robots, once loyal servants, now slaughter us. Our cars, planes, and starships have become machines of death. Cyborgs roam the land, deforming humans, growing their twisted army. </p> <p>Is a heartless, mechanized hell our future? </p> <p>A faint hope shines. Heroes still fight. Famous names. Einav. Marco. Addy. Lailani. The heroes of the Alien Wars. Names etched in our history, in our hearts. Four friends. Four humans . . . against an army of metal. </p> <p>A shadow has fallen. Humanity must shine brighter than ever before.</p>"; 
